cycling home at 1:00

50:38.338 --> 50:40.675
and 2:00 and 3:00
in the morning.

50:40.708 --> 50:43.377
Even a drunk who says
he saw her catch

50:43.410 --> 50:49.216
the first train to Altmaar
at 6:15, wearing angel wings.

50:49.249 --> 50:54.856
