every tip-off seriously,

50:54.889 --> 50:57.859
you completely lose the plot.

50:57.892 --> 51:02.697
That's just how it is.

51:02.730 --> 51:05.567
And I think
I'm going to call it a day.

51:05.600 --> 51:09.202
Okay. Well, thanks
for coming all this way.

51:09.236 --> 51:11.471
Well, hello there.

